title: Girl, 13, arrested for stabbing murder in Essex
text: 09:36 Boydie88 said: 13 year old girl out with 17 and 20 year old lads on a school night. Very good point. At 13 I suppose children are allowed out until 8pm or so and to a certain extent you can't control who they are with. I'd certainly hope they weren't hanging out with 20 year olds though! On reflection - that says more about the 20 year olds than it does about the 13 year old. Advertisement
